OL,3,CHandling error by ambulance technician
OL,4,Ccontributed to Grandmother's death
OL,6,FThe death of a grandmother was
OL,7,Fcontributed to by an ambulance
OL,8,Ftechnician using the wrong lifting
OL,9,Ftechnique causing her to fall and
OL,10,Fbreak her leg, an inquest has
OL,11,Fconcluded.
OL,13,FDoreen Pilling, 93, died after the
OL,14,Ftechnician attempted to lift her with
OL,15,Fa rolled-up towel instead of following
OL,16,Fthe approved safety procedure and
OL,17,Fusing authorised equipment from the
OL,18,Fambulance.
