OL,3,CHandling error by ambulance technician
OL,4,Ccontributed to Grandmother's death
OL,6,FAs a result of the lift Doreen, from
OL,7,FBurnley, fell to the floor in what was
OL,8,Fdescribed as an "uncontrolled
OL,9,Fdescent", on 3 September 2023, and
OL,10,Ffractured her right leg.
OL,12,FAt the inquest into her death, held at
OL,13,FPreston Coroner's Court on 10 April,
OL,14,FCoroner Christopher Long concluded it
OL,15,Fwas a "culpable human failure which
OL,16,Fcontributed to Doreen's death".
OL,18,FDoreen was taken to the Royal
OL,19,FBlackburn Hospital, where she
OL,20,Fdeveloped pneumonia.
