OL,3,CHandling error by ambulance technician
OL,4,Ccontributed to Grandmother's death
OL,6,FAfter a long stay at Blackburn, and
OL,7,Flatterly Pendle Community Hospital,
OL,8,FDoreen died on 24 October 2023.
OL,10,FIn his narrative conclusion, Coroner
OL,11,FChristopher Long said: "Doreen Pilling
OL,12,Fdied on October 24, 2023, at Royal
OL,13,FBlackburn Hospital.
OL,15,F"An ambulance was called to assist Mrs
OL,16,FPilling at her home as she was unable
OL,17,Fto mobilise.
