OL,3,CHandling error by ambulance technician
OL,4,Ccontributed to Grandmother's death
OL,6,F"She received a fracture of the right
OL,7,Fdistal femur when the crew used an
OL,8,Funapproved method to lift her,
OL,9,Fresulting in an uncontrolled descent
OL,10,Fto the floor, causing the fracture.
OL,12,F"She was taken to hospital where,
OL,13,Fafter a long stay, she remained unwell
OL,14,Fwith very limited mobility, which
OL,15,Fcontributed to the development of
OL,16,Fpneumonia from which she did not
OL,17,Frecover."
