OL,3,CHandling error by ambulance technician
OL,4,Ccontributed to Grandmother's death
OL,6,FChristine Fitzpatrick, 66, Doreen's
OL,7,Fdaughter, said: "As a family we are
OL,8,Fgrateful to the coroner for
OL,9,Fconsidering my mum's care so carefully
OL,10,Fand for reaching this conclusion,
OL,11,Fwhich we believe is the right one.
OL,13,F"Watching my mum suffer for so many
OL,14,Fweeks and die in such an undignified
OL,15,Fand distressing manner was truly
OL,16,Fharrowing, and something we will never
OL,17,Ffully recover from.
