OL,3,CHandling error by ambulance technician
OL,4,Ccontributed to Grandmother's death
OL,6,F"My mum was a lovely lady who gave so
OL,7,Fmuch to her family and local community
OL,8,Fin her life, and she deserved so much
OL,9,Fbetter.
OL,11,F"I hope that changes can be put in
OL,12,Fplace to ensure the same poor care is
OL,13,Fnot repeated for another patient in
OL,14,Fthe same situation."
OL,16,FChristine also raised concerns about
OL,17,FDoreen's hospital treatment, which she
OL,18,Fmade an official complaint about as
OL,19,Fshe felt this was very poor.
