OL,4,Ccontributed to Grandmother's death
OL,6,FA previously fiercely independent
OL,7,FDoreen was a food technology teacher
OL,8,Fat Burnley College during her working
OL,9,Flife where she taught adults with
OL,10,Flearning disabilities.
OL,12,FBefore her death, Doreen lived in her
OL,13,Fown flat in the Townfields retirement
OL,14,Fcomplex in Burnley.
OL,16,FWhile her family helped her with her
OL,17,Fshopping, Doreen cooked all her own
OL,18,Fmeals and enjoyed going out regularly
OL,19,Ffor coffee.
