OL,6,FShe had previously been a Salvation
OL,7,FArmy Soldier after her husband Ken's
OL,8,Fdeath in 2008 and had enjoyed
OL,9,Fdelivering food parcels to Burnley
OL,10,Fpeople on Christmas Day.
OL,12,FMadeleine Langmead, a medical
OL,13,Fnegligence solicitor at JMW who is
OL,14,Fhandling the family's legal case,
OL,15,Fsaid: "I welcome the inquest findings,
OL,16,Fas they give much needed answers to
OL,17,FDoreen's family.
