OL,3,CHandling error by ambulance technician
OL,4,Ccontributed to Grandmother's death
OL,6,F"They witnessed her severe decline and
OL,7,Fthe coroner's conclusion confirms
OL,8,Ftheir belief that this all began with
OL,9,Fthe careless mistake of the ambulance
OL,10,Ftechnician.
OL,12,F"This case highlights the catastrophic
OL,13,Fconsequences that can occur from not
OL,14,Ffollowing safety procedures when
OL,15,Fhandling and lifting patients.
OL,17,F"This reckless approach should never
OL,18,Fhave been taken with any patient, let
OL,19,Falone an elderly person at increased
OL,20,Frisk of breaking a bone.
